{"tid":160030,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下一個關於router既問題...","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T12:07:49.000Z","uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b448e5129db809888b30eb324caa693a9ee81c64","tid":160030,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"用緊網上行，modem經常性斷線斷3分鐘左右連番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係modem連番之後router有時要抆電線重開先上得番網，有時又唔洗，係咪router setting有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae91979326f203df37b7a923fba3db4c007beedf","tid":160030,"uid":91203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"啱啱用嗰陣都係咁 過一段時間就會穩定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569c759206699d96144e337728999c40c405eb4d","tid":160030,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱用嗰陣都係咁 過一段時間就會穩定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個router已經用左起碼3年，之前無出現過依種情況，但係之前都無近排咁斷線斷得咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e27886a6740aa305f99954d824c1a450cc5d50","tid":160030,"uid":74943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"近排網上行壞壞地"},{"pid":"2de5ef188e1842da8d5f4d3db77c43e7564e4630","tid":160030,"uid":47373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"你係睇modem啲led燈知道自己斷左?"},{"pid":"6470908482bc7311032a473840bcd233cfb31550","tid":160030,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"網上行黎講 最基本就咪用default DNS Server 轉左做8.8.8.8試下先<br />\n佢個modem 都似有問題（應該話根本係） call人上黎屌下先<br />\n換完仲係咁斷下斷下就似係你果頭啲線鋪等唔好"},{"pid":"9fedaad3daf38df0e73d5a906c6c4eddad16e9ff","tid":160030,"uid":86419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊網上行，modem經常性斷線斷3分鐘左右連番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係modem連番之後router有時要抆電線重開先上得番網，有時又唔洗，係咪router setting有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmodem斷完 著返router未必即時拎得返IP 最簡單就重開 ，再唔係就入返router renew IP"},{"pid":"1b4b9c887680328279ab737e9b10f37bd1a3a06f","tid":160030,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排網上行壞壞地</blockquote><br />\n巴打你都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你係睇modem啲led燈知道自己斷左?</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>網上行黎講 最基本就咪用default DNS Server 轉左做8.8.8.8試下先<br />\n佢個modem 都似有問題（應該話根本係） call人上黎屌下先<br />\n換完仲係咁斷下斷下就似係你果頭啲線鋪等唔好</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，我試下轉8.8.8.8先，另外我已經屌過無數咁多次，上到黎淨係話你村係咁架啦，我最多扮野咁幫你換個modem，我話之前都無事係近排先咁，佢就話因為近排落雨浸到出面啲線，又話依家開始凍冷縮熱漲先咁（對上一次call果陣岩岩開始入冬)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>modem斷完 著返router未必即時拎得返IP 最簡單就重開 ，再唔係就入返router renew IP</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係咁，下次再斷試下得唔得，唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4739efb54cecbad14b532b8668c0538a9437cc3d","tid":160030,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"🤗"}]}